text: Just catching up with my modeller now about the helicopter and he definitely thinks poly model is the way to go :) if you want to send images of your model or ref over i can get some more detailed feedback :)
Hey Craig, thanks for getting back to me on the catch up with work. Absolutely, I'll send you some screen shots of the progress I'm currently on and send you ref I'm using to help me build.

The one thing I am struggling with is the body. As it's very rounded, the rest is flat surfaces so I am able to go through that okay. But I have been experimenting with the correct method, but poly is the best approach
I hope work is fine on your end and production wise is going good. I understand your busy and look forward to hearing back soon.
